column3: Lakme 9 to 5 Weightless Mousse Lip & Cheek Color, Coffee Lite, 9 g
column5: I have bought one more piece of blush velvet even as the first one still has some mousse left in it. Initially I thought this is dry and not enough inside the case but I was wrong.  There is a good quantity inside. I love this beautiful shade and am relieved to have found a shade, I like on my lips, after trying out many others. It is a pleasant colour close to natural nude with ..... perfect as daywear, office wear and even as party wear and even with gloss it does not look loud. The mousse is easy to apply with the applicator  and the weightless formula leaves behind a perfect layer of intense color. Single swipe is enough The finish is powdery matte so I "always" moisturise my lips or else it feels very dry. If you take care to hydrate the lips it stays put comfortably for up to 5-6 hours. The shade will look great on all skin colors. What's more is that it can be a blush.... so easy to apply ..... as it is a powdery weightless mousse. I even used it as eye shadow ! I highly recommend Hope my review is helpful to you! Thanks for reading it üòä

column3: Lakme 9 to 5 Weightless Mousse Lip & Cheek Color, Coffee Lite, 9 g
column5: First of all, The texture of this lip and cheek color is soft, smooth, and mousse like. True to its name, it is absolutely weightless. It applies evenly and smoothly on the lips. The creamy formula settles down to a matte texture in seconds and does not move at all. It is super pigmented, and one swipe is quite enough to cover up even pigmented lips. It does not feel heavy or patchy at any point of time. For a change, it has a pleasant vanilla scent rather than the usual weird Lakme lipstick scent. Rose Touch a beautiful everyday wear shade. This is a perfect rosy-mauve sort of shade and it suits all the skin tones be it lighter or deeper, it looks polished and gorgeous! Used as a blush it gives a stunning rosy flush to the cheeks. I am absolutely in love with colour, I kind of wear it all the time. üòõ It stays 4-5 hours, then it starts to fade from the center. But if you eat oily food, it removes the lipstick from your lips, Sad! Other than that, its a next to perfect affordable Lip Colour. I will try other shades as well. Highly recommended. üëçüëçüëç

column3: Lakme 9 to 5 Weightless Mousse Lip & Cheek Color, Coffee Lite, 9 g
column5: It is not at all smudge proof or transfer proof. It only last until you eat ar drink something. The shade and pigmentation is very good. But nowadays when we have to wear a mask daily, it becomes useless. It may be used as a blush or even as an eyeshadow. But for lips, it is now useless.

column3: Lakme 9 to 5 Weightless Mousse Lip & Cheek Color, Coffee Lite, 9 g
column5: After watching YouTube reviews and Swatch for this shade I ordered it and yes there was a bit difference when you see the shade in actual and on screen, In the picture I have applied a single coat, it is highly pigmented, very light on lips and it's a unique shade. I have always been into pinks and peaches and nudes so this is definitely the shade that will bring you out of the same look and try something bold...still it's the one you can wear daily, goes great with party looks also. What more to ask for. A complete shade. Other shades in sale were for 353 but this one i bought for 469. Maybe it's in the newly added ones, that's why . However in stores you will get on MRP 625. Expiry date is also mentioned below. It's transfer proof and goes long enough if you are not having oily food...moist and creamy texture. Not patchy at all. It's a velvet finish , somewhere in between matte and satin. Which is wonderful. Loved it!! Thank you Amazon, please bring more sale so we can buy more shades of this range ;)

column3: Lakme 9 to 5 Weightless Mousse Lip & Cheek Color, Coffee Lite, 9 g
column5: Beautiful brown shade. Packaging is sleek. But u cant tell the differnt shades apart as its an opaque tube. Shade name is written on the bottom Applicator is sturdy. Does the job. Pointed tip for better application. Colour is beautiful dark brown ( as d name suggest cocoa colour bit softer - and hence d name coco soft, i guess) I m of wheatish complexion, it suits me. Formula is creamy, takes about a minute to completely dry matte finish( ditto like NYX soft matte lip cream). Its not too drying ( as all matte liquid lipsticks are) as colorbar and sugar liquid lippies. People with dry lips problem should moisturize well with lip balms prior use) Smudge proof after drying. I quite like it. Overall great one. Would love to try other shades too.

column3: L'Oreal Paris True Match Super Blendable Natural Liquid Foundation - Rose Vanilla 2R2C2K, 30ml Natural Finish
column5: Unlike all times, the packing for such a good product was of very low quality. Even for Rs.50 product Amazon used to provide excellent care in packing. Also the product was tampered. I been using this product for quite some time. Its comes with a very good packing by loreal with an extremely thick plastic wrap around it. This product did not have any loreal packing at all. Also the seal was neatly broken. The original consitence is very paste like and it does not easy flows off. But stays neatly in our finger tips and that makes in convenient to apply. But this one has a very watery consistency.  Just flows of like a drop and I felt it as atleast 40% diluted. I request Amazon does some mystery shopping works and ensure the quality of the products. I'm worried if this is locally made and that will damage my skin badly. Please let me know what to do this product. Request to provide with the original one.

column3: L'Oreal Paris True Match Super Blendable Natural Liquid Foundation - Rose Vanilla 2R2C2K, 30ml Natural Finish
column5: This is my foundation destination. After trying everything I got my match. My skin tone is neither warm nor cool. It is not even normal. It has olive undertone which makes me look warm and cool according to the light i am in. I have been able to decide whether I am dusky or a bit weatish. On occasion when super exposed to sunlight or too much lightening i look a bit on the other side of weatish that you can call fair. PS: i am sorry if i sound racist here. So then i watched all the youtube vedios of the ladies that had been featured for particular shade and i thought of going for w3. I have no complains with the foundation whatsoever, it blends like magic. Has sparkling shimmer which helps hide fine lines, true as it says. My skin looked flawless. I had never thought that foundation could be a thing for my super dry skin. Fit me, which is again from l'oreal does not supply the dew finish which is for dry skin. Hoping to try it soo. I am so lazy, i've got tons of products to review at my blog and i have just started. For now i am posting the images of the foundation. I have taken it in broad daylight. I have not applied anything to my neck. I am not even cleaned or taken a shower:D Hope this helps. :)

column5: This is my foundation destination. After trying everything I got my match. My skin tone is neither warm nor cool. It is not even normal. It has olive undertone which makes me look warm and cool according to the light i am in. I have been able to decide whether I am dusky or a bit weatish. On occasion when super exposed to sunlight or too much lightening i look a bit on the other side of weatish that you can call fair. PS: i am sorry if i sound racist here. So then i watched all the youtube vedios of the ladies that had been featured for particular shade and i thought of going for w3. I have no complains with the foundation whatsoever, it blends like magic. Has sparkling shimmer which helps hide fine lines, true as it says. My skin looked flawless. I had never thought that foundation could be a thing for my super dry skin. Fit me, which is again from l'oreal does not supply the dew finish which is for dry skin. Hoping to try it soo. I am so lazy, i've got tons of products to review at my blog and i have just started. For now i am posting the images of the foundation. I have taken it in broad daylight. I have not applied anything to my neck. I am not even cleaned or taken a shower:D Hope this helps. :)

column5: - It's liquid base gives normal coverage. But if you are looking for full coverage than you should look for cream based foundation. - It's good for daily wear as it's light weight. - Stays for 4-5 hours if you are not exposed to sun. - Blends with skin well. Doesn't leave patchy skin. - Good product for everyday use.

column3: L'Oreal Paris True Match Super Blendable Natural Liquid Foundation - Rose Vanilla 2R2C2K, 30ml Natural Finish
column5: Unlike all times, the packing for such a good product was of very low quality. Even for Rs.50 product Amazon used to provide excellent care in packing. Also the product was tampered. I been using this product for quite some time. Its comes with a very good packing by loreal with an extremely thick plastic wrap around it. This product did not have any loreal packing at all. Also the seal was neatly broken. The original consitence is very paste like and it does not easy flows off. But stays neatly in our finger tips and that makes in convenient to apply. But this one has a very watery consistency.  Just flows of like a drop and I felt it as atleast 40% diluted. I request Amazon does some mystery shopping works and ensure the quality of the products. I'm worried if this is locally made and that will damage my skin badly. Please let me know what to do this product. Request to provide with the original one.
